ref%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatgpt-claude-gemini-features-comparison-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ewe%20break%20it%20all%20down%20here%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUltimately%2C%20this%20could%20mark%20a%20new%20era%20of%20chatbot%20monogamy.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20signs%20point%20to%20AI%20giants%20pushing%20for%20more%20of%20a%20commitment%20from%20users.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETheir%20top%20models%20all%20sit%20behind%20paywalls%2C%20with%20the%20gap%20between%20premium%20and%20free%20versions%20continuing%20to%20grow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20companies%20are%20also%20under%20considerable%20pressure%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-profitability-analyst-investor-opinions-funding-ipo-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Edemonstrate%20a%20viable%20business%20model%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20potentially%20ahead%20of%20a%20public%20debut.%20A%20stable%20base%20of%20paid%20subscribers%20is%20a%20lot%20more%20appetizing%20to%20investors%20than%20a%20bunch%20of%20non-committal%20freeloaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUsers%20also%20might%20gravitate%20toward%20a%20preferred%20chatbot.%20As%20experimentation%20fades%20into%20practical%20use%2C%20navigating%20multiple%20AI%20chats%20to%20be%20productive%20doesn't%20feel%20%E2%80%A6%20productive.%20And%20if%20it's%20not%20free%2C%20are%20you%20really%20willing%20to%20pay%20for%20multiple%20subscriptions%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhich%20brings%20us%20back%20to%20Anthropic.%20The%20fight%20with%20the%20DoD%20is%20a%20perfect%20way%20to%20try%20and%20juice%20customer%20acquisition%20efforts.%20There%20are%20plenty%20of%20concerns%20about%20AI%20use.%20Anthropic%20can%20pitch%20itself%20as%20a%20safe%20antidote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20catering%20to%20that%20crowd%20could%20prove%20challenging%20as%20competition%20ramps%20up%20and%20pressure%20to%20move%20quickly%20intensifies.%20Anthropic%2C%20which%20was%20founded%20on%20the%20proper%20development%20of%20AI%2C%20already%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-changing-safety-policy-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eweakened%20its%20foundational%20safety%20principle%20last%20week%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-openai-chatgpt-claude-katy-perry-pentagon-subscription-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772542604000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a6060fd3e2f1aef369d842%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-openai-chatgpt-claude-katy-perry-pentagon-subscription-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20AI%20giants%20behind%20two%20of%20the%20world's%20most%20popular%20chatbots%2C%20Claude%20and%20ChatGPT%2C%20have%20escalated%20their%20beef.%20Now%20people%20are%20picking%20sides.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ddefrancesco%40businessinsider.com%20(Dan%20DeFrancesco)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-openai-chatgpt-claude-katy-perry-pentagon-subscription-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20quit%20my%20MBB%20consulting%20job%20to%20help%20others%20land%20jobs%20at%20top%20firms.%20Here's%20what%20separates%20the%20candidates%20who%20get%20offers.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jack%20Kim%20at%20a%20restaurant%20holding%20chopsticks.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a644c41fb3fcb42648c97e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223213%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJack%20Kim%20said%20he%20had%20a%20hard%20time%20getting%20a%20job%20in%20consulting%20because%20he%20overlooked%20the%20%26quot%3Bairplane%20test.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EJack%20Kim%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EJack%20Kim%20struggled%20to%20break%20into%20consulting%20but%20eventually%20landed%20at%20an%20MBB%20firm.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EKim%20quit%20his%20job%20at%20Bain%20to%20co-found%20a%20mentorship%20company%20that%20helps%20others%20get%20consulting%20roles.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EKim%20said%20passing%20the%20%26quot%3Bairplane%20test%26quot%3B%20is%20key%20to%20getting%20an%20offer.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20is%20an%20as-told-to%20essay%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Jack%20Kim%2C%20a%20former%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsunny-stroeer-bain-consultant-quit-burnout-outdoor-adventure-business-athlete-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EBain%20%26amp%3B%20Company%20consultant%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20who%20co-founded%20Casebuddy%2C%20a%20consulting%20mentorship%20program.%20This%20story%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20really%20hard%20for%20me%20to%20break%20into%20consulting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20went%20to%20London%20School%20of%20Economics%2C%20where%20I%20did%20my%20bachelor's%20and%20master's%2C%20and%20then%20I%20started%20at%20a%20consulting%20firm%20called%20Parthenon%2C%20which%20is%20now%20part%20of%20EY.%20I%20worked%20there%20for%20about%20a%20year%20and%20a%20half%20and%20then%20interviewed%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmbb-explained-mckinsey-bain-bcg-compare-big-three-strategy-consultants-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMBB%20firms%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20ultimately%20joining%20Bain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20stayed%20at%20Bain%20for%20three%20and%20a%20half%20years%20and%20got%20two%20promotions%20in%20that%20time.%20Last%20August%20was%20my%20last%20month%20in%20consulting.%20I%20knew%20I%20didn't%20see%20myself%20doing%20consulting%20for%20a%20long%20time.%20I%20never%20really%20saw%20myself%20becoming%20a%20partner%2C%20and%20I%20always%20wanted%20to%20do%20something%20entrepreneurial.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20friend%20was%20already%20running%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-break-into-management-consulting-career-coach-mbb-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ementorship%20business%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20so%20I%20decided%20to%20join%20him.%20I'd%20mentored%20loads%20of%20students%20from%20high%20school%20all%20the%20way%20to%20university%20and%20work%2C%20so%20I%20decided%20to%20give%20it%20a%20go.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20offer%20a%20one-on-one%20mentorship%20program%20that%20takes%20students%20from%20A%20to%20Z%2C%20from%20the%20very%20beginning%20of%20resume%20writing%20and%20cover%20letters%20all%20the%20way%20to%20networking%2C%20behaviorals%2C%20and%20case%20interviews.%20The%20cost%20of%20the%20mentorship%20program%20varies%20because%20everyone's%20on%20a%20different%20timeline%20and%20has%20different%20priorities.%20It%20ranges%20between%201%2C000%20pounds%2C%20or%20about%20%241%2C300%2C%20all%20the%20way%20up%20to%205%2C000%20plus%20pounds%2C%20or%20around%20%246%2C700%2C%20in%20super%20niche%20customized%20cases.%20Most%20of%20the%20students%20will%20land%20in%20between.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20first%20cohort%20that%20we%20launched%20last%20year%20had%20fewer%20than%2010%20students.%20We%20got%20four%20of%20them%20into%20a%20top%20consulting%20firm%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmbb-leaders-consulting-firms-advising-leaders-and-ceos-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMcKinsey%2C%20Bain%2C%20or%20BCG%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20one%20of%20them%20actually%20came%20from%20a%20non-target%20university.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20our%20second%20quarter%20this%20year%2C%20we've%20had%20over%201%2C000%20people%20apply%20to%20the%20mentorship%20program%2C%20which%20I'm%20super%20grateful%20for%2C%20but%20we%20only%20take%2010%20to%2015%20people%20because%20we%20want%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20we%20provide%20dedicated%20support%20to%20each%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20people%20are%20finding%20us%20through%20my%20social%20media%20presence%2C%20mostly%20YouTube%2C%20which%20I%20started%20building%20while%20I%20was%20still%20a%20consultant.%20It%20is%20small%20but%20growing.%20I%20also%20posted%20consistently%20on%20TikTok%20and%20Instagram%20last%20year%2C%20and%20hosted%20a%20free%20webinar%20that%20500%20people%20signed%20up%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20reason%20I%20left%20consulting%20was%20the%20feeling%20of%20fulfillment.%20Whilst%20I%20did%20enjoy%20the%20interactions%20and%20the%20people%20in%20consulting%2C%20I'm%20a%20very%20results-oriented%20person%2C%20and%20seeing%20the%20results%20of%20my%20students%20getting%20their%20jobs%20makes%20me%20feel%20fulfilled%20and%20happy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2258f56358-7e80-4e9e-9ff3-e5ed1ec5764e%5C%22%3EI%20didn't%20land%20a%20job%20in%20consulting%20right%20away%20because%20I%20overlooked%20the%20'airplane%20test'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20my%20final%20year%20of%20university%2C%20I%20failed%20seven%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbain-consulting-tips-for-getting-job-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efinal%20round%20interviews%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20think%20it%20mostly%20came%20down%20to%20the%20%26quot%3Bairplane%20test.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20really%20underestimated%20the%20importance%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdiary-of-a-ceo-steven-bartlett-hiring-tips-culture-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eculture%20fit%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20behavioral%20interviews%2C%20which%20is%20what%20resulted%20in%20those%20failures.%20After%20not%20getting%20an%20offer%2C%20I%20had%20to%20go%20back%20to%20school%20to%20do%20a%20master's%2C%20which%20obviously%20cost%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20again%2C%20but%20then%20I%20finally%20got%20a%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20researched%20online%2C%20everyone%20talked%20about%20acing%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmckinsey-interview-case-study-ai-test-bcg-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecase%20interviews%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20but%20no%20one%20really%20highlighted%20the%20importance%20of%20the%20behavioral%20interview.%20So%20I%20always%20overlooked%20that%2C%20and%20I%20think%20that's%20what%20made%20me%20essentially%20delay%20my%20consulting%20journey%20for%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3Bairplane%20test%26quot%3B%20is%20a%20consulting%20terminology%20used%20in%20hiring.%20We%20travel%20a%20lot%20for%20our%20projects.%20So%20what%20we%20think%20about%20is%3A%20Can%20I%20sit%20next%20to%20this%20candidate%20on%20an%20airplane%20for%2012%20hours%2C%20and%20would%20I%20be%20comfortable%20and%20have%20fun%20doing%20it%3F%20Because%20I'm%20going%20to%20be%20doing%20that%20every%20single%20week%20on%20a%20travel%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPassing%20this%20test%20will%20help%20you%20get%20the%20offer%3A%20Do%20I%20find%20this%20person%20comfortable%3F%20Do%20I%20like%20this%20person%20enough%20to%20see%20them%20in%20our%20team%3F%20And%20ultimately%2C%20next%20to%20my%20seat%20on%20an%20airplane.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20especially%20important%20at%20the%20final%20round%20of%20the%20hiring%20process.%20Everyone's%20going%20to%20be%20really%20good%20at%20cases%20by%20the%20time%20you%20reach%20the%20final%20round.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20it%20comes%20down%20to%20executive%20communication%2C%20being%20able%20to%20hold%20a%20conversation%20with%20senior%20partners%2C%20and%20at%20the%20same%20time%20just%20being%20likable%20and%20being%20a%20joy%20to%20be%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fex-mbb-consultant-says-getting-job-offer-is-about-the-airplane-test-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772541841000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a644c41fb3fcb42648c97e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.