ectly%20assist%20Americans%20in%E2%80%AFdeparting%E2%80%AFIsrael%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20US%20Embassy%20in%20Jerusalem%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20embassy%20shared%20that%20the%20Israeli%20Ministry%20of%20Tourism%20was%20operating%20shuttles%20to%20a%20border%20crossing%20between%20Egypt%20and%20Israel%20at%20the%20town%20of%20Taba.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20choose%20to%20avail%20yourself%20of%20this%20option%20to%20depart%2C%20the%20US%20government%20cannot%20guarantee%20your%20safety%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20US%20embassy%2C%20adding%20that%20they%20were%20sharing%20the%20information%20%26quot%3Bas%20a%20courtesy%20to%20those%20wishing%20to%20leave%20Israel.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Qatar%2C%20where%20Iranian%20retaliatory%20strikes%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fqatarenergy-pauses-production-after-iranian-strikes-hit-energy-facilities-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehit%20key%20energy%20facilities%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20country's%20US%20embassy%20issued%20a%20travel%20advisory%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20also%20warning%20American%20citizens%20they%20were%20unable%20to%20help%20them%20evacuate%2C%20saying%20that%20they%20should%20%26quot%3Btake%20advantage%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwealthy-people-dubai-abu-dhabi-chartering-planes-evacuate-middle-east-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecommercial%20transportation%20options%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20embassy%20in%20Qatar%20advised%20Americans%20who%20chose%20to%20stay%20to%20create%20a%20contingency%20plan%2C%20but%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bthese%20alternative%20plans%20should%20not%20rely%20on%20the%20US%20government%20for%20assisted%20departure%20or%20evacuation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIran%20has%20launched%20a%20barrage%20of%20retaliatory%20missiles%20against%20US%20allies%20in%20the%20region%2C%20hitting%20sites%20including%20US%20military%20bases%2C%20Dubai's%20Burj%20Al%20Arab%20hotel%2C%20and%20the%20US%20embassy%20in%20Riyadh.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20list%20of%20countries%20Americans%20are%20being%20urged%20to%20depart%20from%20immediately%20is%20as%20follows%3A%20Bahrain%2C%20Egypt%2C%20Iran%2C%20Iraq%2C%20Israel%2C%20the%20West%20Bank%2C%20and%20Gaza%2C%20Jordan%2C%20Kuwait%2C%20Lebanon%2C%20Oman%2C%20Qatar%2C%20Saudi%20Arabia%2C%20Syria%2C%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%2C%20and%20Yemen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIran%2C%20Iraq%2C%20Kuwait%2C%20Bahrain%2C%20and%20Qatar%20have%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstrikes-on-iran-flights-canceled-diverted-busiest-airspace-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eclosed%20their%20airspaces%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20Tuesday%2C%20Dubai%20International%20has%20resumed%20limited%20flight%20services%20but%20continues%20to%20instruct%20travelers%20not%20to%20come%20to%20the%20airport%20unless%20their%20flight%20has%20been%20confirmed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWealthy%20travelers%20and%20expats%20in%20the%20UAE%20have%20turned%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwealthy-people-dubai-abu-dhabi-chartering-planes-evacuate-middle-east-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprivate%20jets%20and%20chauffeured%20drivers%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20help%20them%20flee%20the%20region%2C%20but%20many%20have%20been%20caught%20up%20in%20lengthy%20border%20crossings%20amid%20the%20rush%20to%20Saudi%20Arabia%20and%20Oman%2C%20where%20some%20flights%20were%20still%20departing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMonica%20Marks%2C%20a%20professor%20at%20NYU%20Abu%20Dhabi%2C%20posted%20on%20X%2C%20wondering%20how%20Americans%20are%20supposed%20to%20leave%20the%20Middle%20East%20without%20government%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplatform.twitter.com%2Fwidgets.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquot