h%20back%20to%20growth%20this%20year%2C%20and%20reinforcing%20my%20confidence%20in%20the%20momentum%20we're%20building%20and%20the%20future%20we're%20creating%20together%2C%26quot%3B%20Fiddelke%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnalysts%20said%20ahead%20of%20the%20earnings%20release%20that%20Fiddelke%20and%20his%20team%20have%20their%20work%20cut%20out%20for%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTime%20is%20Target's%20greatest%20adversary%2C%26quot%3B%20Mizuho%20analyst%20David%20Bellinger%20said%20in%20a%20weekend%20note%20ahead%20of%20the%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20senior%20management%20is%20taking%20the%20necessary%20steps%20to%20re-position%20the%20business%2C%20others%20are%20not%20standing%20still%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%2C%20referring%20in%20particular%20to%20Walmart%2C%20which%20has%20been%20gaining%20momentum%20as%20Target%20struggles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUltimately%2C%20the%20company%20needs%20to%20show%20how%20it%20can%20better%20compete%20and%20define%20its%20place%20in%20the%20market%2C%26quot%3B%20UBS%20analyst%20Michael%20Lasser%20said%20in%20a%20note%20leading%20up%20to%20the%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFiddelke%20is%20set%20to%20unveil%20his%20larger%20turnaround%20strategy%20Tuesday%20morning%20at%20Target's%20headquarters%20in%20Minneapolis.%20One%20month%20into%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftarget-ceo-michael-fiddelke-busy-first-weeks-on-the-job-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehis%20new%20role%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20CEO%20has%20said%20he's%20focused%20on%20four%20key%20priorities%3A%20improving%20the%20merchandising%2C%20elevating%20the%20shopping%20experience%2C%20investing%20in%20tech%2C%20and%20supporting%20workers%20and%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20also%20said%20it%20was%20seeing%20strong%20recent%20performance%20in%20non-merchandise%20sales%2C%20including%20its%20Roundel%20ads%20business%2C%20Target%20Plus%20membership%2C%20and%20same-day%20delivery%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E