GAUTAM%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Stripe%20CEO's%20AI-era%20software%20pitch%3A%20Start%20serving%20it%20like%20pizza%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224252%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Stripe%20Co-founder%20and%20CEO%20Patrick%20Collison%20delivers%20his%20keynote%20conference%20during%20day%20three%20of%20the%20Mobile%20World%20Congress%20at%20the%20Fira%20Gran%20Via%20complex%20in%20Barcelona%2C%20Spain%20on%20February%2024%2C%202016.%20The%20annual%20Mobile%20World%20Congress%20hosts%20some%20of%20the%20world's%20largest%20communication%20companies%2C%20the%20show%20runs%20from%20the%2022%20to%2025%20February.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a61594d3e2f1aef369da0d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222835%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EStripe%20CEO%20Patrick%20Collison%20advocates%20for%20on-demand%20software%20in%20the%20AI%20era%20on%20the%20TBPN%20podcast.%3Cp%3EAOP.Press%2FCorbis%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EStripe%20CEO%20Patrick%20Collison%20advocated%20for%20on-demand%20software%20in%20the%20AI%20era%20on%20the%20%26quot%3BTBPN%26quot%3B%20podcast.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAnthropic's%20Claude%20AI%20update%20sparked%20a%20software%20stock%20selloff%2C%20impacting%20SaaS%20business%20models.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENvidia%20CEO%20Jensen%20Huang%20dismissed%20fears%20of%20AI%20replacing%20traditional%20software%20tools%20industry.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EStripe's%20CEO%2C%20Patrick%20Collison%2C%20delivered%20a%20provocative%20thesis%20about%20the%20future%20of%20software%20in%20the%20age%20of%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAppearing%20on%20the%20%26quot%3BTBPN%26quot%3B%20podcast%20last%20week%2C%20Collison%20told%20show%20hosts%20John%20Coogan%20and%20Jordi%20Hays%20that%20software%20shouldn't%20be%20mass-produced%20but%20created%20on%20demand%20instead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSoftware%20should%20be%20like%20pizza%2C%20and%20it%20should%20be%20cooked%20right%20then%20and%20there%20at%20the%20moment%20of%20use%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Collison.%20%26quot%3BUp%20until%20now%2C%20the%20economics%20of%20software%20have%20been%20conceived%20as%20fixed%20cost%20and%20then%20infinitely%20monetized.%26quot%3B%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%26quot%3BOnce%20there%20are%20inference%20costs%20and%20custom%20creation%20involved%2C%20it%20really%20shifts%2C%26quot%3B%20Collison%20added.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20kind%20of%20the%20non-Walrasian%20software%20regime.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECollison's%20analogy%20echoes%20a%20broader%20tension%20gripping%20the%20technology%20industry%20on%20whether%20AI%20tools%20could%20replace%2C%20rather%20than%20just%20augment%2C%20traditional%20software.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20anxiety%20briefly%20turned%20into%20market%20reality%20earlier%20in%20February.%20Releases%20and%20updates%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fclaude-ai-tools-tech-selloff-software-apocalypse-cybersecurity-anthropic-ibm-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAnthropic's%20Claude%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20especially%20enterprise-focused%20capabilities%20like%20Claude%20Cowork%20and%20the%20automation%20plugin%2C%20triggered%20a%20deep%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-today-selloff-tariffs-trump-software-ai-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eselloff%20in%20software%20stocks%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20investors%20fretted%20that%20AI%20could%20automate%20tasks%20that%20once%20required%20licensed%20software%20or%20human%20expertise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20selloff%20wiped%20out%20billions%20in%20market%20value%2C%20with%20broad%20software%20ETFs%20and%20enterprise%20names%20sliding%20sharply%2C%20as%20investors%20interpreted%20Claude's%20expanding%20abilities%20as%20a%20threat%20to%20traditional%20SaaS%20business%20models%20that%20count%20on%20recurring%20licensing%20revenues.%20The%20iShares%20Expanded%20Tech%20Software%20Sector%20ETF%20is%20down%20nearly%2030%25%20since%20the%20beginning%20of%202026%20as%20of%20March%202.%20IBM%20is%20seeing%20some%20of%20the%20heaviest%20losses%20among%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fibm-stock-price-anthropic-ai-update-cobol-language-software-selloff-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esoftware%20companies%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20recording%20its%20worst%20slide%20in%2026%20years%20as%20the%20stock%20fell%2013%25%20on%20February%2023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20stock%20slide%20aside%2C%20not%20everyone%20is%20sold.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsoftware-selloff-reactions-jensen-huang-steven-sinofsky-arm-ceo-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENvidia%20CEO%20Jensen%20Huang%3C%2Fa%3E%20pushed%20back%20on%20the%20idea%20that%20the%20tool%20industry%20is%20in%20decline%20and%20will%20be%20replaced%20by%20AI%20at%20a%20recent%20Cisco%20AI%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20could%20tell%20because%20there's%20a%20whole%20bunch%20of%20software%20companies%20whose%20stock%20prices%20are%20under%20a%20lot%20of%20pressure%20because%20somehow%20AI%20is%20going%20to%20replace%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Huang.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20the%20most%20illogical%20thing%20in%20the%20world%2C%20and%20time%20will%20prove%20itself.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-stripe-ceo-floats-creating-software-on-demand-sell-off-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772537041000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a615b01fb3fcb42648c7ed%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-stripe-ceo-floats-creating-software-on-demand-sell-off-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Patrick%20Collison%20said%20that%20software%20should%20be%20made%20on%20demand%20%26quot%3Blike%20pizza%26quot%3B%20amid%20fears%20that%20