ses%20them%2C%20as%20do%20partners.%20Ukraine%20relies%20heavily%20on%20the%20weapon%20to%20defeat%20Russian%20barrages.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20and%20its%20allies%20are%20shooting%20down%20Iranian%20missile%20and%20drone%20bombardments%20with%20air%20defense%20interceptors%2C%20leaning%20hard%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fproduction-of-patriot-missiles-surging-demand-exceptionally-high-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EPatriot%20missiles%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20critical%20weapon%20that%20was%20already%20in%20high%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20start%20of%20Israel's%20Operation%20Roaring%20Lion%20and%20America's%20Operation%20Epic%20Fury%20on%20Saturday%2C%20which%20saw%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftop-us-general-rundown-opening-days-iran-attack-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estrikes%20across%20Iran%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Tehran%20retaliated%20with%20its%20own%20strikes%2C%20lobbing%20missiles%20into%20nations%20supporting%20US%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmerican%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-forces-air-defense-battles-fight-with-iran-official-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eair%20defenders%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20turned%20to%20their%20MIM-104%20Patriot%20batteries%2C%20Terminal%20High%20Altitude%20Area%20Defense%20batteries%2C%20and%20ship-launched%20Standard%20Missile-series%20interceptors%20to%20down%20incoming%20Iranian%20threats%20%E2%80%94%20both%20missiles%20and%20drones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20battles%20would%20draw%20on%20US%20stocks%20of%20Patriot%20Advanced%20Capability-3%20(PAC-3)%20missiles%2C%20among%20other%20weapons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUS%20allies%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20including%20Qatar%2C%20Bahrain%2C%20Kuwait%2C%20and%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%2C%20also%20operate%20Patriot%20missile%20system%20variants%2C%20and%20these%20countries%20have%20been%20actively%20involved%20in%20the%20air%20defense%20fight%20against%20Iranian%20weapons%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20volume%20of%20weaponry%20Iran%20has%20fired%20at%20other%20countries%20over%20the%20past%20few%20days%20is%20significant.%20Kuwait%20said%20Sunday%20it%20had%20already%20faced%2097%20ballistic%20missiles%20and%20283%20drones%2C%20demonstrating%20a%20demand%20for%20extensive%20air%20defense%20arsenals%20to%20keep%20up%20the%20fight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225625%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Soldiers%20from%20the%2011th%20Air%20Defense%20Artillery%20Brigade%20conduct%20a%20Patriot%20missile%20live-fire%20exercise%20at%20MacGregor%20Range%20near%20Fort%20Bliss%2C%20Texas%2C%20August%2023%2C%202025.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F698e0dc5a645d1188189399f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223750%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOne%20Patriot%20PAC-3%20interceptor%20costs%20%243.7%20million.%3Cp%3EUS%20Army%20photo%20by%20Sgt.%20JaDarius%20Duncan%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20outcome%20of%20the%20conflict%20with%20Iran%2C%20expected%20to%20potentially%20last%20for%20several%20weeks%2C%20could%20be%20determined%20in%20part%20by%20which%20runs%20out%20first%2C%20Iran's%20missiles%20or%20the%20interceptor%20arsenals%20of%20the%20air%20defenders%20on%20the%20opposite%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeth%20Jones%2C%20president%20of%20the%20defense%20and%20security%20department%20at%20the%20Center%20for%20Strategic%20and%20International%20Studies%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fknpr.org%2F2026-03-01%2Fwhat-is-the-u-s-militarys-capacity-to-carry-out-extended-strikes-in-iran%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%20NPR%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20reality%20is%20neither%20Israel%20nor%20the%20United%20States%20have%20sufficient%20munitions%2C%20either%20offensive%20or%20defensive%2C%20for%20a%20war%20that%20really%20lasts%20weeks%20into%20months.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20demand%20for%20Patriot%20interceptors%20and%20other%20air%20defense%20weaponry%20in%20this%20conflict%2C%20likely%20more%20than%20one%20interceptor%20per%20threat%2C%20adds%20greater%20strain%20to%20already-insufficient%20missile%20stockpiles%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eand%20industry%20scrambling%20to%20meet%20rising%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUS%20officials%20and%20war%20experts%20have%20said%20demand%20for%20Patriots%20and%20other%20interceptors%20is%20surging%2C%20and%20while%20companies%2C%20like%20the%20Patriot%20interceptor%20producer%20Lockheed%20Martin%2C%20are%20tremendously%20ramping%20up%20production%2C%20the%20process%20can%20take%20years%2C%20making%20it%20hard%20to%20keep%20pace.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20media%20reports%20have%20signaled%20that%20the%20stockpiles%20of%20Patriot%20interceptors%20are%20running%20low.%20The%20Pentagon%20challenged%20the%20reporting%20at%20one%20point%20last%20year%2C%20saying%20%26quot%3Bthe%20US%20military%20has%20what%20it%20needs%20to%20fight%20and%20win%20any%20mission%2C%20anywhere%2C%20any%20time.%26quot%3B%20Yet%20the%20Department%20of%20Defense%20is%20also%20trying%20to%20dramatically%20boost%20production.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine%20has%20been%20a%20major%20source%20of%20growing%20demand%20for%20Patriots%2C%20considered%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20best%20air%20defense%20systems.%20It%20relies%20on%20the%20weapons%20to%20fend%20off%20regular%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-mixes-missile-tactics-ukraine-feeds-intel-to-patriot-makers-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ERussian%20barrages%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20messages%20to%20reporters%2C%20Ukrainian%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelenskyy%20said%20%26quot%3Bit%20is%20too%20early%20to%20draw%20conclusions%26quot%3B%20about%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20conflict%20with%20Iran%20on%20Patriot%20interceptor%20availability%2C%20but%20%26quot%3Bif%20there%20are%20prolonged%20hostilities%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20this%20will%20certainly%20affect%20supplies.%20I%20am%20confident%20of%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20said%20it%20was%20hard%20to%20get%20Patriots%20to%20Ukraine.%20He%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bwe%20need%20them%20too.%26quot%3B%20In%20the%20current%20Iran%20fight%2C%20just%20a%20few%20days%20into%20the%20conflict%2C%20he%20signaled%20that%20the%20US%20military%20may%20need%20to%20draw%20from%20global%20munitions%20stocks%20to%20keep%20up%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Soldiers%20from%20the%2011th%20Air%20Defense%20Artillery%20Brigade%20conduct%20a%20Patriot%20missile%20live-fire%20exercise%20at%20MacGregor%20Range%20near%20Fort%20Bliss%2C%20Texas%2C%20Aug.%2023%2C%202025.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F695d73cb832e0ef1ead7478d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELockheed%20Martin%20said%20it%20plans%20to%20boost%20production%20of%20Patriot%20missile%20interceptors.%3Cp%3EUS%20Army%20photo%20by%20Sgt.%20JaDarius%20Duncan%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMajor%20production%20contracts%20have%20shown%20that%20there%20is%20a%20need%20for%20more%20of%20these%20weapons.%20Lockheed%20Martin's%20PAC-3%20production%20has%20continued%20to%20increase%20since%20hitting%20500%20in%202024%2C%20while%20other%20defense%20firms%20are%20also%20increasing%20related%20production.%20A%20recent%20agreement%20said%20that%20over%20a%20seven-year%20period%2C%20Lockheed%20aims%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flockheed-says-it-will-ramp-up-patriot-missile-production-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eboost%20Patriot%20interceptor%20production%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20600%20to%202%2C000%20annually.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Army%20began%20pursuing%20efforts%20last%20year%20to%20expand%20its%20purchase%20of%20interceptors%20with%20plans%20to%20invest%20more%20than%20%241%20billion%20in%20Patriot%20missiles%20alone%20and%20an%20objective%20of%2013%2C773%20total%20missiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20PAC-3%20interceptor%20costs%20roughly%20%243.7%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProcurement%20data%20for%20the%20PAC-3%20missile%2C%20compiled%20and%20analyzed%20by%20CSIS%2C%20show%20that%20between%20fiscal%20years%202015%20and%202024%2C%20the%20Pentagon%20purchased%20an%20average%20of%20nearly%20270%20missiles%20annually.%20CSIS%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.csis.org%2Fanalysis%2Fdepleting-missile-defense-interceptor-inventory%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enoted%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20steps%20such%20as%20the%20Army's%20decision%20to%20raise%20its%20Patriot%20buy%20quantities%20help%20send%20a%20sustained%2C%20reliable%20demand%20signal%20to%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConflicts%20elsewhere%20make%20it%20hard%20to%20build%20up%20deep%20stockpiles.%20The%20US%20needs%20them%2C%20and%20numerous%20partner%20nations%20need%20them.%20Without%20sufficient%20stocks%2C%20the%20US%20runs%20the%20risk%20of%20being%20drawn%20into%20a%20high-end%20conflict%20with%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-burned-through-more-tomahawks-iran-may-need-for-china-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Enear-peer%20foe%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20adversary%20like%20China%2C%20without%20enough%20air%20defenses%2C%20leaving%20it%20in%20a%20dangerous%20position%20in%20a%20missile%20fight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChina%20will%20be%20keen%20for%20Iran%20to%20fight%20it%20out%20against%20America%2C%26quot%3B%20observed%20Mick%20Ryan%2C%20a%20retired%20Australian%20general%20and%20strategist%20focused%20on%20future%20warfare.%20%26quot%3BThe%20more%20munitions%20America%20uses%20in%20Iran%2C%20and%20the%20more%20strategic%20attention%20America%20pays%20to%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20the%20happier%20the%20CCP%20is%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20Chinese%20Communist%20Party.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20late%202024%2C%20Navy%20Adm.%20Samuel%20Paparo%2C%20head%20of%20US%20Indo-Pacific%20Command%2C%20said%20ongoing%20fighting%20in%20Ukraine%20and%20around%20the%20Middle%20East%20had%20%26quot%3Beaten%20into%26quot%3B%20Patriot%20stockpiles%20needed%20in%20his%20area%20of%20responsibility%2C%20%26quot%3Band%20to%20say%20otherwise%20would%20be%20dishonest.%26quot%3B%20A%20conflict%20of%20this%20new%20one's%20intensity%2C%20which%20is%20expected%20to%20see%20an%20uptick%2C%20may%20only%20exacerbate%20the%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ECorrespondent%20Jake%20Epstein%20contributed%20to%20this%20report.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpatriot-missiles-fired-in-iran-war-stressing-strained-stockpile-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772534221000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a5fcccd3e2f1aef369d723%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpatriot-missiles-fired-in-iran-war-stressing-strained-stockpile-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22US%20officials%20have%20expressed%20concerns%20on%20Patriot%20interceptor%20stockpiles%20as%20recent%20conflicts%20have%20seen%20reliance%20on%20the%20system.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22cpanella%40businessinsider.com%20(Chris%20Panella)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpatriot-missiles-fired-in-iran-war-stressing-strained-stockpile-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'No%20better%20feeling'%3A%20149%20Indians%20fly%20home%20from%20Dubai%20on%20Air%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772534066000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-128966125%2Cimgsize-1086530.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fno-better-feeling-air-india-flies-149-stranded-passengers-to-delhi-from-dubai-amid-escalating-west-asia-tensions%2Farticleshow%2F128964012.cms%22%2C%22