far-fetched%20%E2%80%94%20science%20fiction%20for%20managers%2C%20and%20a%20due%20diligence%20horror%20story%20for%20allocators.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBack%20then%2C%20institutional%20investors%20wanted%20to%20see%20a%20real%20back%20office%20%E2%80%94%20finance%2C%20operations%2C%20compliance%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20expensive%20technology%20necessary%20to%20run%20sophisticated%20risk%2C%20trading%2C%20and%20reporting.%20Even%20seasoned%20portfolio%20managers%20typically%20needed%20a%20team%20before%20big%20investors%20would%20buy%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20future%20is%20here%20for%20portfolio%20managers%2C%20and%20allocators%20are%20seeing%20dollar%20signs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20ask%20Ben%20Williams%2C%20who%20launched%20Bayhunt%20Capital%20in%202024%20as%20the%20founder%2C%20chief%20investment%20officer%2C%20and%20sole%20employee.%20The%20firm%2C%20based%20in%20Marin%20County%2C%20California%2C%20focuses%20on%20real%20estate%20stocks%20and%20manages%20%24360%20million%2C%20including%20leverage%2C%20for%20allocators%20through%20individual%20investment%20portfolios%2C%20known%20in%20the%20industry%20as%20separately%20managed%20accounts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20always%20been%20something%20in%20the%20back%20of%20my%20mind%20that%20I%20wanted%20to%20do%20%E2%80%94%20have%20my%20own%20business%2C%26quot%3B%20Williams%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20Now%20about%20a%20year%20into%20live%20trading%2C%20he%20said%20he's%20on%20the%20cusp%20of%20onboarding%20his%20first%20employee%2C%20an%20investment%20analyst.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20five%20years%20ago%2C%20Williams%20couldn't%20have%20imagined%20some%20of%20the%20industry%20shifts%20that%20made%20it%20possible%20to%20start%20a%20company%20this%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELeaner%2C%20faster%20launches%20like%20Bayhunt's%20are%20one%20of%20the%20knock-on%20effects%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhedge-fund-sma-gold-rush-will-intensify-2026-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20booming%20popularity%20of%20separately%20managed%20accounts%3C%2Fa%3E.%20As%20allocators%20increasingly%20lean%20into%20SMAs%20for%20the%20transparency%20and%20control%20they%20provide%2C%20managers%20have%20been%20able%20to%20launch%20with%20a%20smaller%20headcount%20%E2%80%94%20and%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20without%20a%20commingled%20fund%20at%20all.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20cloud-based%20tech%20systems%20and%20outsourced%20service%20providers%20have%20made%20it%20possible%20to%20rent%20much%20of%20the%20infrastructure%20that%20used%20to%20require%20an%20in-house%20build.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222100%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ben%20Williams%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a5c7bafd4fbd083f295935%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBen%20Williams%20founded%20Bayhunt%20Capital%20in%202024%2C%20managing%20investor%20capital%20as%20the%20sole%20employee.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Ben%20Williams%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHedge%20funds%2C%20which%20have%20had%20a%20generational%20run%20of%20returns%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20are%20now%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftop-hedge-fund-strategies-allocators-love-for-2026-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20clear%20favorite%20among%20investors%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20and%20a%20growing%20number%20of%20portfolio%20managers%20like%20Williams%20are%20concluding%20there's%20never%20been%20a%20better%20time%20to%20take%20the%20plunge%20and%20pursue%20the%20dream%20of%20running%20their%20own%20fund.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESS%26amp%3BC%2C%20a%20top%20software%20and%20service%20provider%20to%20hedge%20funds%2C%20has%20seen%20a%20marked%20uptick%20in%20adoption%20of%20its%20cloud-based%20investment%20platform%20geared%20toward%20emerging%20managers.%20The%20number%20of%20clients%20using%20the%20platform%2C%20called%20Eze%20Eclipse%2C%20has%20grown%20more%20than%2025%25%20since%202024%2C%20with%2070%20new%20joiners%20in%202025%2C%20the%20company%20told%20Business%20Insider%2C%20attributing%20the%20acceleration%20in%20part%20to%20firms%20streamlining%20operations%20for%20SMAs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20whole%20cottage%20industry%20of%20service%20providers%20is%20popping%20up%20and%20scrambling%20to%20meet%20the%20needs%20of%20these%20upstart%20firms.%20IIP%20Services%20launched%20in%202024%20with%20a%20focus%20on%20the%20burgeoning%20SMA%20market.%20With%20more%20managers%20launching%20at%20smaller%20sizes%2C%20IIP%20saw%20an%20opportunity%20to%20provide%20a%20soup-to-nuts%20product%20for%20the%20non-investment%20aspects%20of%20the%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESemi%20Gogliormella%2C%20a%20partner%20at%20IIP%20Services%20who%20has%20held%20senior%20operations%20and%20compliance%20roles%20at%20firms%20including%20WorldQuant%20and%20Boulder%20Hill%2C%20says%20many%20PMs%20are%20realizing%20that%20the%20combined%20power%20of%20the%20SMA%20market%20and%20improved%20technology%20has%20significantly%20reduced%20the%20time%20to%20get%20a%20firm%20off%20the%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he%20has%20seen%20managers%20up%20and%20running%20with%20new%20SMA%20capital%20within%20weeks%20of%20signing%20an%20investment%20management%20agreement%2C%20though%20he%20cautioned%20that%20it%20isn't%20the%20norm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOnboarding%20and%20going%20live%20gets%20truncated%20significantly%2C%26quot%3B%20Gogliormella%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220cc0eb96-50a3-48f4-8064-ffffa040bc41%5C%22%3EThe%20Substack%20effect%2C%20but%20for%20portfolio%20managers%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20meteoric%20growth%20this%20decade%20of%20multistrategy%20hedge%20funds%20like%20Citadel%2C%20Millennium%2C%20and%20Point72%2C%20and%20the%20ensuing%20war%20for%20talent%2C%20has%20created%20more%20opportunities%20than%20ever%20for%20portfolio%20managers%20to%20gain%20experience%20and%20a%20taste%20of%20running%20their%20own%20business.%20A%20major%20allure%20of%20these%20firms%20is%20that%20the%20platform%20handles%20operational%20headaches%20and%20red%20tape%2C%20leaving%20investors%20to%20focus%20on%20markets%2C%20supported%20by%20world-class%20technology%20and%20trading%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReplicating%20that%20experience%20outside%20of%20the%20confines%20of%20a%20pod%20shop%20wasn't%20realistic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESuperstars%20could%20spin%20out%20and%20raise%20the%20capital%20to%20build%20and%20hire%20%E2%80%94%20a%20lengthy%20endeavor%20%E2%80%94%20but%20for%20most%20managers%2C%20a%20%26quot%3Bcareer%20change%26quot%3B%20meant%20hopping%20to%20another%20multistrat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20that%20small%2C%20stand-alone%20money%20managers%20didn't%20previously%20exist.%20It's%20that%20now%20they%20can%20attract%20institutional%20capital%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20economics%20that%20come%20with%20it%20%E2%80%94%20and%20more%20easily%20recreate%20the%20systems%20used%20by%20large%20funds%2C%20offering%20a%20career%20path%20many%20might%20not%20otherwise%20have%20considered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20unlike%20how%20Substack%20and%20its%20competitors%20offered%20better%20professional%20tools%20for%20writers%20to%20self-publish%2C%20distribute%2C%20and%20monetize%20their%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20these%20managers%2C%20they're%20incubating%20in%20these%20multistrats%20and%20have%20a%20good%20pedigrees%20when%20they%20spin%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20James%20Griffin%2C%20global%20head%20of%20sales%20for%20SS%26amp%3BC%20wealth%20and%20investment%20technology%20group.%20%26quot%3BTheir%20expectations%20are%20that%20they're%20going%20to%20get%20the%20same%20bells%20and%20whistles%20that%20they've%20had%20at%20these%20big%20institutions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMultistrats%20have%20become%20significant%20SMA%20allocators%20in%20their%20own%20right%2C%20and%20some%20offer%20access%20to%20their%20in-house%20tools%20and%20systems%20as%20an%20inducement%20or%20in%20exchange%20for%20a%20fee%20discount%2C%20industry%20sources%20said.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EBut%20for%20those%20without%20that%20option%20%E2%80%94%20or%20who%20are%20looking%20for%20more%20independence%20and%20fewer%20strings%20%E2%80%94%20managers%20with%20less%20than%20%24100%20million%20in%20capital%20can%20rent%20the%20same%20tech%20stack%20as%20some%20multibillion-dollar%20pod%20shops%2C%20Griffin%20said%2C%20noting%20that%20his%20firm%20provides%20software%20to%20some%20of%20the%20industry's%20largest%20funds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVeteran%20systematic%20portfolio%20managers%20Matt%20Gormley%20and%20Matt%20Isherwood%20began%20looking%20to%20set%20up%20their%20own%20shop%20about%20five%20years%20ago%2C%20when%20the%20SMA%20rush%20was%20starting%20to%20take%20shape.%20They%20went%20in-house%20at%20Walleye%2C%20leaving%20two%20years%20later%20to%20launch%20Brabus%20Capital.%20Like%20Bayhunt%2C%20London-based%20Brabus%20started%20small%20and%20exclusively%20with%20SMA%20capital%2C%20but%20it%20is%20growing%20and%20is%20in%20the%20process%20of%20bringing%20on%20staff%20for%20key%20investor%20relations%20and%20technology%20roles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20of%20the%20challenges%20for%20systematic%20investing%20is%20the%20barriers%20to%20entry%20are%20high%2C%20which%20is%20why%20quants%20tend%20to%20be%20tied%20up%20in%20multistrats%2C%26quot%3B%20Gormley%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20duo%20started%20exploring%20options%20to%20outsource%20components%20of%20the%20business%20and%20realized%20the%20landscape%20had%20changed%20significantly%20since%202020.%20Abundant%20SMA%20capital%20meant%20they%20could%20start%20running%20money%20faster.%20They%20could%20also%20rent%20state-of-the-art%20technology%2C%20compliance%20and%20operational%20infrastructure%2C%20cybersecurity%2C%20and%20hire%20someone%20to%20manage%20relationships%20with%20prime%20and%20execution%20brokers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20Williams%2C%20they%20signed%20on%20with%20IIP%2C%20which%20aims%20to%20save%20managers%20time%20and%20money%20getting%20off%20the%20ground%20by%20purchasing%20institutional-grade%20software%20%E2%80%94%20order%2C%20execution%2C%20and%20portfolio%20management%20systems%20%E2%80%94%20at%20wholesale%20prices%20and%20integrating%20them%20into%20a%20cohesive%2C%20ready-to-use%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20enabled%20us%20to%20get%20scale%20from%20day%20one%20that%20would%20typically%20take%2012%20to%2018%20months%20to%20build%20if%20you%20were%20recreating%20the%20multistrat%20setup%20from%20scratch%2C%26quot%3B%20Gormley%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227b672376-93e1-4491-adca-d08f1c201537%5C%22%3EYou%20can%20rent%20infrastructure%3B%20you%20can't%20rent%20credibility%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDon't%20let%20the%20small%20headcounts%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20relative%20ease%20of%20getting%20these%20firms%20off%20the%20ground%20%E2%80%94%20fool%20you.%20This%20isn't%20trading%20from%20your%20couch%20in%20your%20pajamas%2C%20and%20cheaper%20technology%20doesn't%20mean%20launching%20a%20hedge%20fund%20is%20now%20fair%20game%20for%20anyone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExperience%2C%20talent%2C%20and%20credibility%20are%20still%20prerequisites.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20Bayhunt%20and%20Brabus%20said%20their%20comfort%20outsourcing%20non-investment%20work%20came%20from%20years%20inside%20institutional%20platforms%2C%20gaining%20exposure%20to%20the%20less%20glamorous%20but%20nevertheless%20critical%20functions%20of%20hedge%20fund%20%E2%80%94%20risk%2C%20operations%2C%20controls%2C%20and%20due%20diligence.%20Williams%2C%20who%20liaised%20with%20several%20risk%20managers%20at%20top-tier%20multistrats%2C%20said%20that%20while%20the%20technology%20is%20cheaper%20and%20more%20available%20than%20it%20was%20a%20decade%20ago%2C%20%26quot%3Ba%20person%20needs%20to%20have%20a%20considerable%20amount%20of%20experience%26quot%3B%20to%20understand%20the%20risk%20math%20and%20to%20have%20the%20confidence%20to%20strike%20out%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrabus'%20founders%20put%20it%20more%20bluntly%3A%20you%20can%20outsource%20the%20plumbing%2C%20but%20you%20can't%20outsource%20knowing%20whether%20it's%20working%20%E2%80%94%20and%20allocators%20still%20aren't%20writing%20meaningful%20checks%20without%20a%20credible%20track%20record%20and%20an%20operation%20that%20can%20survive%20institutional%20due%20diligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20with%20high-quality%20outsourced%20partners%2C%20running%20a%20hedge%20fund%20business%20is%20a%20big%20lift%20if%20you%20don't%20understand%20what%20goes%20on%20downstream%20from%20your%20investment%20process%2C%26quot%3B%20Isherwood%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flean-hedge-fund-launches-sma-boom-technology-outsourcing-2026-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772533921000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a5c833d3e2f1aef369d0c4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flean-hedge-fund-launches-sma-boom-technology-outsourcing-2026-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Lean%20hedge%20fund%20launches%20like%20Bayhunt%20Capital%20are%20thriving%20with%20minimal%20headcount%20with%20the%20help%20of%20SMAs%20and%20next-generation%20technology.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22amorrell%40businessinsider.com%20(Alex%20Morrell)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flean-hedge-fund-launches-sma-boom-technology-outsourcing-2026-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20sanctions%20Rwanda's%20military%20and%20top%20commanders%20over%20fighting%20in%20DR%20Congo%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772533812000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F1671%2Flive%2Fe6785de0-16d1-11f1-be34-99a23f225661.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcr5l7zdnjgpo%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rwanda%20accused%20Washington's%20move%20as%20%E2%80%9Cone%20sided%E2%80%9D%20and%20politically%20motivated.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcr5l7zdnjgpo%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Former%20Goldman%20CEO%20Lloyd%20Blankfein%20says%20markets%20are%20due%20for%20a%20'reckoning%2C'%20and%20private%20credit%20could%20be%20the%20catalyst%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Llody%20Blankfein%20speaking%20on%20stage%20at%20an%20event%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a5d0f9fd4fbd083f295a4b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EMichael%20Cohen%2FGetty%20Images%20for%20The%20New%20York%20Times%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EFormer%20Goldman%20CEO%20Lloyd%20Blankfein%20says%20he's%20worried%20markets%20are%20headed%20for%20a%20%26quot%3Bmore%20severe%20reckoning.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20spoke%20of%20the%20growing%20risks%20of%20another%20financial%20crisis%2C%20and%20pointed%20to%20problems%20in%20private%20credit.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EInvestors%20may%20realize%20one%20day%20that%20assets%20in%20the%20sector%20are%20mispriced%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20executive%20who%20led%20Goldman%20Sachs%20through%20the%20Great%20Financial%20Crisis%20is%20sounding%20a%20warning%20about%20America's%20private%20credit%20machine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-economy-outlook-crisis-debt-private-credit-lloyd-blankfein-goldman-sachs-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ELloyd%20Blankfein%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20former%20CEO%20of%20Goldman%20Sachs%2C%20said%20he's%20worried%20about%20problems%20brewing%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprivate-credit-financial-contagion-risk-software-ai-selloff-2026-2%5C%22