figcaption%3EA%20commercial%20ship%20anchors%20off%20the%20coast%20of%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%20amid%20disruptions%20in%20the%20Strait%20of%20Hormuz%2C%20a%20key%20shipping%20passage%20in%20the%20Middle%20East.%3Cp%3EStringer%2FAnadolu%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EWar%20with%20Iran%20has%20already%20rattled%20markets%2C%20with%20volatility%20hitting%20stocks%20and%20oil%20prices%20jumping.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EJefferies%20said%20that%20the%20conflict%20could%20lift%20the%20metals%20and%20mining%20sector.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAnalysts%20also%20say%20the%20geopolitical%20upheaval%20is%20bullish%20for%20gold%20and%20aluminum.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fcommodities%2Foil-price%3Ftype%3Dwti%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EOil%3C%2Fa%3E%20isn't%20the%20only%20commodity%20that%20will%20see%20prices%20rise%20amid%20the%20war%20with%20Iran.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Jefferies%20analysts%2C%20commodities%20more%20broadly%20could%20spike%20on%20the%20latest%20geopolitical%20upheaval%2C%20with%20some%20specific%20metals%20and%20also%20stocks%20in%20the%20metals%20and%20mining%20sector%20poised%20to%20gain.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20has%20been%20our%20view%20that%20strength%20in%20metals%20%26amp%3B%20mining%20share%20prices%20over%20the%20past%206%2B%20months%20could%20be%20attributed%20to%20elevated%20geopolitical%20risks%2C%20a%20structurally%20weakening%20dollar%20and%20the%20risk%20of%20inflation%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bank%20wrote%20on%20Monday.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20its%20top%20stock%20picks%20in%20the%20space%20and%20what%20it%20sees%20for%20commodities%20like%20gold%20and%20aluminum.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22373f7c7a-c385-4081-a639-4510c8db0148%5C%22%3ETop%20stock%20picks%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EJefferies%20reiterated%20its%20bullish%20stance%20on%20the%20metals%20and%20mining%20sector%2C%20flagging%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Ffcx-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EFreeport%20McMoRan%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fglcnf-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGlencore%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fanglo_american_6-stock%3FmiRedirects%3D1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAnglo%20American%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20its%20top%20stock%20picks%20in%20the%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20nodded%20to%20Alcoa%20as%20a%20possible%20top%20pick%2C%20depending%20on%20how%20long%20the%20war%20goes%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYet%2C%20the%20analysts%20went%20on%20to%20note%20that%20the%20conflict%20should%20lift%20the%20space%20broadly%2C%20laying%20out%20three%20impacts%20it%20sees%20from%20the%20conflict%3Arising%20costs%20due%20to%20climbing%20energy%20prices%2C%20supply%20chain%20risks%2C%20and%20an%20intensified%20need%20for%20strategic%20stockpiling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d9e7cd50-14a9-4447-983e-f3863cb42b89%5C%22%3ESupply-disruption%20risk%20is%20bullish%20for%20aluminum%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fcommodities%2Faluminum-price%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAluminum%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20in%20focus%20as%20the%20Middle%20East%20has%20emerged%20as%20a%20major%20producer%20since%20the%20mid-2000s.%20The%20closure%20of%20the%20Strait%20of%20Hormuz%20or%20any%20major%20supply%20chain%20disruptions%20would%20directly%20impact%20the%20aluminum%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERoughly%209%25%20of%20global%20aluminum%20production%20is%20from%20Gulf%20states%2C%20which%20rely%20on%20the%20Strait%20of%20Hormuz%20for%20shipments%2C%20according%20to%20Jefferies%20research.%20The%20analysts%20also%20highlight%20that%20Iran%20alone%20accounts%20for%20around%203%25%20of%20global%20iron%20ore%20production.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJPMorgan%20commodities%20analysts%20say%20that%20aluminum%20supply%20disruptions%20are%20a%20%26quot%3Bmajor%20bullish%20risk%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20metal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStockpiling%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20could%20also%20prove%20bullish%20for%20copper%2C%20which%20recently%20saw%20an%20uptick%20alongside%20precious%20gold%20and%20silver%20in%20the%20latter%20half%20of%202025.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f92be4cb-3767-4c4d-afd7-0bd26d589992%5C%22%3EGold%20gains%20as%20a%20safe%20haven%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fcommodities%2Fgold-price%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EThe%20price%20of%20gold%3C%2Fa%3E%20jumped%20as%20a%20new%20geopolitical%20conflict%20reiterated%20one%20of%20the%20metal's%20big%20bull%20cases%2C%20which%20has%20helped%20it%20soar%20to%20records%20over%20the%20last%20year.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20acknowledged%20that%20a%20stronger%20dollar%20resulting%20from%20the%20war%20could%20keep%20a%20lid%20on%20prices%2C%20as%20the%20dollar%20and%20commodities%20tend%20to%20be%20inversely%20correlated%2C%20but%20said%20the%20bull%20case%20remains%20strong.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20we%20believe%20the%20geopolitical%20and%20inflation%20factors%20matter%20more%20than%20the%20stronger%20dollar%20for%20now%2C%20and%20commodity%20prices%20should%20rise%20as%20a%20result%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20added.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJPMorgan%20analysts%20said%20that%20gold%20futures'%20positioning%20indicates%20a%20potential%205%25%20to%2010%25%20upside%20in%20prices%20in%20the%20near%20term.%20They%20noted%2C%20however%2C%20that%20%26quot%3BConflict-driven%20risk%20premiums%20in%20gold%20can%20be%20sharp%20but%20hard%20to%20sustain.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Firan-attacks-metals-mining-stocks-top-picks-commodities-gold-fcx-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772532901000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F