tegy-consultants-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebiggest%20consulting%20firms%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20proxies%20in%20their%20battle%20to%20control%20the%20lucrative%20enterprise%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20this%20week%20announced%20multi-year%20partnerships%20with%20Boston%20Consulting%20Group%2C%20McKinsey%20%26amp%3B%20Company%2C%20Accenture%2C%20and%20Capgemini%3Cstrong%3E%3Cs%3E%20%3C%2Fs%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3Eto%20help%20companies%20integrate%20AI%20into%20existing%20systems%2C%20rethink%20workflows%2C%20and%20deploy%20AI%20coworkers%20at%20scale%20alongside%20OpenAI%20engineers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWorking%20side%20by%20side%20with%20OpenAI%20enhances%20our%20ability%20to%20help%20companies%20reimagine%20their%20business%20to%20capture%20more%20value%20from%20AI%2C%26quot%3B%20Ben%20Ellencweig%2C%20a%20McKinsey%20senior%20partner%2C%20said%20in%20a%20press%20release%20announcing%20the%20partnership.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20partnerships%20will%20help%20each%20firm%20deploy%20AI%20coworkers%20across%20the%20enterprise%2C%20according%20to%20OpenAI's%20blog%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%2F%2Fembed.typeform.com%2Fnext%2Fembed.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20data-tf-live%3D%5C%2201KEYWXWNGAX9X498G9BJDYJXB%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EAnthropic%20has%20made%20similar%20moves.%20Last%20year%2C%20the%20OpenAI%20rival%20rolled%20out%20its%20own%20slate%20of%20consulting%20partnerships%20to%20accelerate%20enterprise%20adoption.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20December%2C%20it%20teamed%20up%20with%20Accenture%20to%20help%20%26quot%3Benterprises%20move%20from%20AI%20pilots%20to%20full-scale%20deployment.%26quot%3B%20Two%20months%20earlier%2C%20it%20struck%20a%20deal%20with%20Deloitte%20to%20make%20Claude%20available%20across%20the%20firm's%20global%20network%20and%20launched%20a%20certification%20program%20to%20train%2015%2C000%20Deloitte%20staffers%20on%20the%20model%20to%20build%20AI%20solutions%20for%20clients%20in%20regulated%20industries%2C%20from%20financial%20services%20to%20healthcare%20and%20life%20sciences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20partnerships%20underscore%20how%20important%20it%20is%20to%20the%20leading%20AI%20labs%20that%20companies%20adopt%20their%20tools.%20OpenAI%20is%20racing%20to%20show%20revenue%20growth.%20Anthropic%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20has%20long%20made%20enterprise%20a%20cornerstone%20of%20its%20long-term%20strategy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnthropic%20has%20been%20rapidly%20expanding%20its%20direct%20enterprise%20offerings.%20This%20month%2C%20it%20introduced%20a%20new%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-ai-software-claude-microsoft-powerpoint-excel-slack-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esuite%20of%20AI%20tools%3C%2Fa%3E%20designed%20to%20help%20Claude%20operate%20inside%20popular%20workplace%20applications%20like%20Microsoft%20Excel%20and%20PowerPoint.%20It's%20also%20up%20against%20tech%20giants%20like%20Microsoft%20and%20Google%2C%20which%20already%20control%20much%20of%20the%20workplace%20software%20that%20corporate%20clients%20rely%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20these%20partnerships%20underscore%20a%20two-way%20shift.%20As%20AI%20startups%20look%20to%20consultancies%20for%20distribution%20and%20credibility%2C%20consulting%20firms%20are%20simultaneously%20reworking%20their%20own%20models%20to%20stay%20competitive%20in%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmckinsey-chief-ai-cutting-adding-jobs-growth-ai-agents-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI-driven%20market%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConsulting%20firms%20have%20pivoted%20hard%20since%20AI%20blew%20onto%20the%20scene%20with%20the%20release%20of%20OpenAI's%20ChatGPT%20in%202022%2C%20and%20these%20partnerships%20are%20just%20one%20way%20they%20are%20evolving%20to%20shore%20up%20their%20business.%20The%20big%20consulting%20firms%20say%20AI%20will%20soon%20make%20up%20a%20significant%20share%20of%20their%20client%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20McKinsey%2C%20where%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmckinsey-workforce-ai-agents-consulting-industry-bob-sternfels-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20agents%20are%3C%2Fa%3E%20rapidly%20multiplying%20alongside%20its%2040%2C000-person%20workforce%2C%20senior%20partners%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20roughly%2040%25%20of%20the%20firm's%20work%20is%20now%20analytics-%20or%20AI-related%20and%20shifting%20toward%20generative%20AI.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBCG%2C%20too%20%E2%80%94%20where%20nearly%2090%25%20of%20its%2033%2C000%20employees%20use%20AI%20%E2%80%94%20says%20it%20has%20created%20more%20custom%20GPTs%20than%20any%20other%20OpenAI%20customer%2C%20with%20five%20times%20as%20many%20employees%20building%20them%20as%20a%20year%20ago%2C%20according%20to%20Alicia%20Pittman%2C%20the%20head%20of%20BCG's%20global%20people%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20hype%20around%20AI%20consultants%20told%20Business%20Insider%20there%20is%20still%20a%20long%20way%20to%20go%20before%20these%20tools%20are%20embedded%20in%20consulting%20firms'%20workflows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEveryone%20has%20Copilot%2C%20and%20everyone%20has%20GPT%20or%20Claude%2C%26quot%3B%20Mina%20Alaghband%2C%20a%20former%20McKinsey%20partner%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BI%20would%20say%20at%20McKinsey%2C%20there%20are%20some%20use%20cases%20where%20those%20tools%20are%20applicable%2C%20but%20there%20are%20many%20where%20they%20are%20not%20sufficiently%20enterprise-grade.%20They%20don't%20have%20sufficient%20guardrails.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESomething%20to%20share%20about%20how%20consultants%20are%20using%20AI%3F%20Business%20Insider%20would%20like%20to%20hear%20from%20you.%20Email%20Lakshmi%20Varanasi%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Alvaranasi%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Elvaranasi%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%