startups%2C%20including%20Gecko%20Robotics%2C%20Abridge%2C%20and%20Skild%20AI.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EPittsburgh's%20new%20mayor%20is%20personally%20cold-calling%20upwards%20of%2020%20founders%20and%20CEOs%20across%20the%20country%20every%20week%20to%20check%20in%20on%20them%2C%20or%20to%20convince%20them%20to%20move%20to%20his%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20people%20think%20it's%20a%20prank%20call%2C%20but%20for%20others%2C%20it's%20like%2C%20'wow%2C%20the%20mayor%20of%20Pittsburgh%20just%20called%2C'%26quot%3B%20said%20Corey%20O'Connor%2C%20who%20estimates%20he%20has%20called%20around%20150%20people%20since%20taking%20office%20in%20January.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20already%20here%2C%20I%20ask%2C%20'How%20can%20we%20help%20you%20expand%3F'%20If%20you're%20not%20here%2C%20I%20ask%20'How%20do%20we%20get%20you%20to%20come%20to%20Pittsburgh%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPittsburgh%20has%20historically%20been%20known%20as%20%26quot%3Bthe%20Steel%20City%26quot%3B%20and%20is%20home%20to%20the%20Pittsburgh%20Steelers.%20O'Connor's%20father%20worked%20as%20a%20steelworker%20before%20a%20long%20career%20in%20city%20politics.%20However%2C%20as%20O'Connor%20is%20quick%20to%20point%20out%2C%20there%20are%20no%20longer%20any%20steel%20mills%20within%20city%20limits%2C%20while%20the%20area%20is%20home%20to%20some%20of%20the%20most%20important%20startups%20in%20the%20U.S.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20predictions%20of%20its%20waning%20influence%20during%20the%20Covid%20era%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20wildly%20off%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-ceo-san-francisco-is-back-ai-boom-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20Bay%20Area's%20tech%20scene%20is%20now%20hotter%20than%20ever%2C%20%3C%2Fa%3Elargely%20thanks%20to%20AI.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcalifornia-miami-south-florida-billionaires-wealth-tax-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EThat%20has%20not%20stopped%20smaller%20cities%20like%20Miami%20and%20Austin%20from%20trying%20to%20grab%20VC%20dollars%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20especially%20as%20the%20cost%20of%20living%20in%20California%20skyrockets.%20Now%2C%20Pittsburgh%20would%20like%20to%20be%20the%20next%20Miami.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIts%20startups%20raised%20%241.48%20billion%20in%202025%2C%20still%20a%20fraction%20of%20major%20tech%20hubs%2C%20but%20the%20region's%20strongest%20venture%20capital%20year%20since%202019%2C%20according%20to%20PitchBook.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStandouts%20include%20Gecko%20Robotics%2C%20valued%20at%20%241.7%20billion%2C%20which%20builds%20wall-climbing%20robots%20that%20inspect%20critical%20infrastructure%2C%20including%20power%20plants%20and%20industrial%20facilities.%20Abridge%2C%20valued%20at%20%245.3%20billion%2C%20uses%20artificial%20intelligence%20to%20automatically%20generate%20medical%20documentation%20from%20doctor-patient%20conversations.%20It%20has%20emerged%20as%20one%20of%20the%20most%20closely%20watched%20AI%20companies%20in%20healthcare.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20high-profile%20is%20Skild%20AI%2C%20which%20is%20developing%20foundation%20models%20for%20robotics%2C%20training%20AI%20systems%20that%20allow%20machines%20to%20operate%20more%20autonomously%20in%20real-world%20environments.%20The%20company%20raised%20%241.4%20billion%20in%20a%20deal%20led%20by%20SoftBank%20Group%20and%20Nvidia%20in%20January%2C%20pushing%20its%20valuation%20to%20%2415%20billion%2C%20according%20to%20PitchBook.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20goal%20is%20to%20change%20the%20narrative%2C%26quot%3B%20O'Connor%20said%2C%20adding%20he%20will%20use%20every%20opportunity%20he%20can%20get%20to%20tout%20the%20city's%20tech%20potential%2C%20especially%20as%20the%20spotlight%20will%20be%20on%20Pittsburgh%20as%20it%20prepares%20to%20host%20the%20NFL%20Draft%20in%20April.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22099a9836-f85d-4048-9afd-1fc7a117e577%5C%22%3EDeep-seated%20roots%20in%20AI%20and%20robotics%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20city's%20AI%20and%20robotics%20credentials%20stretch%20back%20decades.%20In%20the%201960s%2C%20Carnegie%20Mellon%20professors%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fai.cmu.edu%2Fresearch-and-policy-impact%2Fhistory-of-ai-at-cmu%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebegan%20groundbreaking%20research%20in%20AI.%3C%2Fa%3E%20In%201979%2C%20the%20first%20robotics%20institute%20at%20a%20U.S.%20university%20was%20started%20at%20CMU.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20challenge%20is%20keeping%20the%20most%20talented%20graduates%20from%20bolting%20to%20Silicon%20Valley.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20constantly%20going%20to%20meet%20kids%20on%20campus%2C%26quot%3B%20O'Connor%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAffordability%20is%20a%20key%20selling%20point.%20The%20median%20price%20for%20a%20single-family%20home%20in%20Pittsburgh%20and%20surrounding%20Allegheny%20County%20is%2042.3%20percent%20below%20the%20national%20average.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EO'Connor%20is%20also%20trying%20to%20streamline%20the%20city's%20permitting%20process%20to%20make%20it%20easier%20for%20tech%20companies%20to%20expand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20can%20get%20you%20a%20permit%20in%20four%20to%20five%20weeks%2C%20so%20you%20don't%20have%20to%20wait%20through%20the%20government%20bureaucracy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20January%2C%20Factify%2C%20a%20Tel%20Aviv-based%20digital%20document%20startup%2C%20said%20it%20plans%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffinance.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2Ffactify-raises-73m-build-intelligent-133800253.html%3Fguccounter%3D1%26guce_referrer%3DaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuZ29vZ2xlLmNvbS8%26guce_referrer_sig%3DAQAAAHmCAeWFK8g126Ir5Fwkoj8EvLisRlYluWI-mHsn3w8L2d191cO0lJPW_BsyXFpnJX34WQsdCo9Ok_TVtQws5MVh8XZTCfbEOdTJsedzkb0pVS1e9nEUM5wHqDRmL2DOZ6yuw8wNXzRl4FBAKMVxS6a4ejjM3RGc96m-2OBcf0oY%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexpand%20its%20presence%20in%20Pittsburgh%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20use%20the%20city%20as%20a%20major%20hub%20for%20customer%20engagement%20and%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAsked%20if%20he%20has%20successfully%20convinced%