337000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2026-03%2F7hfilegg_china_625x300_03_March_26.jpg%3Fim%3DFitAndFill%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Firan-israel-war-could-a-burning-middle-east-be-an-opportunity-for-china-11163037%23publisher%3Dnewsstand%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22What%20looks%20like%20a%20setback%20for%20Beijing%20in%20West%20Asia%20might%20actually%20be%20more%20leverage%20-%20a%20chance%20to%20build%20long-term%20capital%20without%20firing%20a%20single%20shot.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Firan-israel-war-could-a-burning-middle-east-be-an-opportunity-for-china-11163037%23publisher%3Dnewsstand%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Dallas%20Fed%20says%20'older%2C%20experienced%20workers'%20likely%20have%20less%20cause%20for%20concern%20about%20AI%20job%20displacement%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20line%20of%20people%2C%20carrying%20folders%20and%20in%20semi-formal%20wear%2C%20outside%20of%20a%20job%20fair.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a5d3e71fb3fcb42648bf98%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENew%20research%20suggests%20that%20longer-tenured%20employees%20have%20seen%20wage%20growth%20since%20ChatGPT%20launched.%20It%20also%20says%20getting%20a%20foot%20in%20the%20door%20is%20harder%20for%20young%20career-seekers.%3Cp%3EJoe%20Raedle%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Dallas%20Fed%20analyzed%20employment%20and%20wage%20trends%20in%20AI-exposed%20industries.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWages%20in%20those%20sectors%20are%20still%20rising%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20in%20roles%20that%20reward%20experience.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EEntry-level%20workers%20appear%20to%20be%20facing%20a%20tougher%20hiring%20market.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EArtificial%20intelligence%20hasn't%20yet%20triggered%20the%20broad%20job%20losses%20many%20feared%20%E2%80%94%20at%20least%20not%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flooking-for-work-harder-havent-changed-jobs-in-years-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eexperienced%20workers%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20the%20takeaway%20from%20a%20new%20analysis%20by%20J.%20Scott%20Davis%2C%20an%20assistant%20vice%20president%20at%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dallasfed.org%2Fresearch%2Feconomics%2F2026%2F0224%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFederal%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20Dallas%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20examined%20employment%20and%20wage%20trends%20in%20industries%20most%20exposed%20to%20artificial%20intelligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDavis%20argues%20the%20data%20tell%20a%20more%20nuanced%20story%20%E2%80%94%20one%20that's%20challenging%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-plan-cut-managers-aws-internal-guidelines-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etraditional%20career%20ladder%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20helping%20older%20employees%20earn%20a%20bit%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20ChatGPT's%20debut%20in%20late%202022%2C%20overall%20US%20employment%20has%20risen%20about%202.5%25%2C%20according%20to%20Davis'%20analysis%2C%20which%20uses%20an%20AI%20exposure%20index%20developed%20by%20researchers%20and%20published%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsms.onlinelibrary.wiley.com%2Fdoi%2Ffull%2F10.1002%2Fsmj.3286%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EStrategic%20Management%20Journal%3C%2Fa%3E.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20employment%20in%20the%20sectors%20most%20exposed%20to%20AI%20has%20slipped%20by%20roughly%201%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWages%20tell%20a%20different%20story.%20The%20average%20weekly%20pay%20nationwide%20has%20climbed%207.5%25%20since%20fall%202022.%20And%20across%20the%20most%20AI-exposed%20industries%2C%20wages%20have%20grown%20faster%2C%20up%208.5%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20AI%20were%20simply%20replacing%20workers%2C%20both%20employment%20and%20wages%20would%20likely%20be%20falling%2C%20Davis%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20Davis%20points%20to%20a%20divide%20between%20%26quot%3Bcodified%26quot%3B%20knowledge%20%E2%80%94%20the%20kind%20learned%20from%20textbooks%20and%20in%20university%20courses%20%E2%80%94%20and%20%26quot%3Btacit%26quot%3B%20knowledge%20gained%20from%20hands-on%20work%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BReturns%20on%20job%20experience%20are%20increasing%20in%20AI-exposed%20occupations%2C%26quot%3B%20Davis%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BYoung%20workers%20with%20primarily%20codifiable%20knowledge%20and%20limited%20experience%20will%20likely%20face%20challenging%20job%20markets.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUsing%20Bureau%20of%20Labor%20Statistics%20data%2C%20his%20analysis%20found%20that%20the%20occupations%20most%20exposed%20to%20AI%20tend%20to%20offer%20larger%20pay%20premiums%20for%20experienced%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20roles%20with%20less%20hands-on%20experience%2C%20AI%20exposure%20is%20associated%20with%20weaker%20wage%20growth%2C%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWorkers%20under%2025%20in%20AI-exposed%20industries%20have%20also%20experienced%20employment%20declines%2C%20according%20to%20Davis'%20analysis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20appears%20to%20be%20less%20cause%20for%20concern%20about%20widespread%20job%20displacement%20for%20older%2C%20experienced%20workers%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e5535ab1-439e-47fc-9d43-16998138fcd9%5C%22%3EA%20less%20dire%20picture%E2%80%A6%20so%20far%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20findings%20offer%20a%20counterpoint%20to%20the%20more%20apocalyptic%20predictions%20about%20AI's%20impact%20on%20the%20labor%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-crash-ai-boom-recession-citrini-research-layoffs-jobs-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECitrini%20Research%20published%20a%20memo%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20written%20from%20the%20hypothetical%20perspective%20in%202028%2C%20that%20theorized%20how%20AI%20could%20crush%20the%20US%20jobs%20market%20and%20trigger%20a%20broad-based%20market%20collapse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20if%20our%20AI%20bullishness%20continues%20to%20be%20right...and%20what%20if%20that's%20actually%20bearish%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20memo%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETop%20executives%20inside%20the%20AI%20companies%20are%20worried%20about%20jobs%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDario%20Amodei%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Anthropic%2C%20the%20company%20that%20runs%20Claude%2C%20warned%20that%20AI%20could%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-ceo-warning-ai-could-eliminate-jobs-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eeliminate%2050%25%20of%20entry-level%3C%2Fa%3E%20office%20jobs.%20OpenAI's%20head%20of%20product%2C%20Olivier%20Godement%2C%20said%20the%20life%20sciences%2C%20customer%20service%2C%20and%20computer%20engineering%20industries%20were%20all%20about%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-exec-3-jobs-ai-risk-automation-olivier-godement-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eget%20automated%3C%2Fa%3E.%20And%20Boris%20Cherny%2C%20the%20creator%20of%20Claude%20Code%2C%20said%20that%20he%20doesn't%20believe%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-claude-code-founder-ai-impacts-software-engineer-role-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ejob%20title%20%26quot%3Bsoftware%20engineer%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20will%20exist%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20now%2C%20at%20least%2C%20the%20Dallas%20Fed%20paints%20a%20different%20picture%20of%20today's%20jobs%20market.%20It%20points%20to%20less%20mass%20displacement%20and%20market%20ruptures%20%E2%80%94%20and%20more%20power%20for%20employees%20who%20already%20have%20their%20foot%20in%20the%20door.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdallas-fed-ai-study-experienced-older-workers-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772531221000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a5d4dfd3e2f1aef369d211%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdallas-fed-ai-study-experienced-older-workers-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20new%20analysis%20from%20the%20Dallas%20Fed%20looks%20at%20the%20jobs%20impact%20since%20ChatGPT's%20launch.%20The%20data%20suggests%20a%20divide%20between%20young%20and%20old%20employees.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22bshimkus%40insider.com%20(Ben%20Shimkus)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdallas-fed-ai-study-experienced-older-workers-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I'm%20a%20single%20mom%2C%20and%20my%20son%20was%20in%20Dubai%20with%20his%20nanny.%20I%20spent%20%242%2C500%20to%20get%20back%20to%20him.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nicky%20Lazou%20with%20her%20son%20and%20dog.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a69e63d3e2f1aef369dccf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221638%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENicky%20Lazou%20said%20she%20spent%20%242%2C500%20to%20get%20back%20to%20her%20son%20in%20the%20UAE.%3Cp%3ENicky%20Lazou%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ENicky%20Lazou%2C%20a%20business%20owner%20based%20in%20Dubai%2C%20was%20in%20London%20for%20work%20when%20the%20Middle%20East%20crisis%20unfolded.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHer%20five-year-old%20son%20was%20with%20his%20nanny%20when%20strikes%20hit%20parts%20of%20Dubai.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20paid%20%242%2C500%20to%20fly%20into%20Oman%20and%20cross%20the%20land%20border%20to%20the%20UAE%20to%20be%20with%20her%20son.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Nicky%20Lazou%2C%2039%2C%20a%20Dubai-based%20beauty%20business%20owner%20and%20a%20single%20mother%20to%20her%20five-year-old%20son.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20traveled%20from%20Dubai%20to%20London%20on%20Friday%20for%20a%20pop-up%20for%20my%20business%2C%20leaving%20my%20five-year-old%20son%20with%20our%20live-in%20nanny.%20Then%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fphotos-damage-luxury-tourism-dubai-fairmont-palm-iran-airstrike-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMiddle%20East%20crisis%3C%2Fa%3E%20unfolded%2C%20my%20return%20flight%20was%20canceled%2C%20and%20I%20scrambled%20to%20get%20back%20into%20the%20UAE.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20been%20living%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstranded-dubai-missile-strikes-canceled-flight-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ein%20Dubai%3C%2Fa%3E%20since%202022%2C%20having%20moved%20from%20the%20UK.%20I%20have%20a%20hair%20and%20beauty%20business%20in%20the%20UAE%20and%20England.%20I'm%20a%20single%20mother%2C%20and%20raising%20my%20son%20in%20Dubai%20felt%20right%20and%20safe%20%E2%80%94%20it%20was%20easy%20for%20me%20to%20get%20nanny%20care%20while%20running%20my%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20traveled%20to%20London%20on%20Friday%20for%20a%20pop-up.%20My%20scheduled%20flight%20back%20would%20have%20been%20on%20Sunday%20at%2010%20p.m.%20after%20I%20finished%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20like%20to%20leave%20my%20son%20for%20too%20long.%20When%20I'm%20away%20from%20him%2C%20my%20nervous%20system%20is%20always%20on%20edge.%20As%20soon%20as%20I%20heard%20about%20the%20crisis%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20I%20thought%2C%20%26quot%3BPlease%20don't%20close%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwealthy-people-dubai-abu-dhabi-chartering-planes-evacuate-middle-east-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20flights%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20they%20did%20anyway.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20I%20was%20outside%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-web-services-data-center-fire-objects-middle-east-strikes-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20UAE%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20was%20getting%20notifications%20on%20my%20local%20phone%20telling%20residents%20to%20stay%20away%20from%20windows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20live%20in%20an%20apartment%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20glass%20and%20windows%2C%20and%20in%20my%20head%2C%20I%20could%20just%20imagine%20my%20little%20boy%20in%20his%20bed%20near%20the%20window.%20Returning%20was%20not%20a%20preference%3B%20it%20was%20a%20responsibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20first%20thought%20was%20that%20I%20had%20to%20get%20back%20to%20him%2C%20no%20matter%20what.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22801186b8-e62a-45e6-b1ff-b80c5fccbb5b%5C%22%3EFlying%20into%20Oman%20and%20crossing%20into%20the%20UAE%20by%20land%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20travel%20agent%20recommended%20going%20through%20Saudi%20Arabia%20or%20driving%20from%20Oman.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20went%20to%20London%20Heathrow%2C%20and%20I%20boarded%20an%20Oman%20Air%20flight.%20The%20one-way%20flight%2C%20eight%20hours%20long%2C%20was%20%C2%A31%2C300%2C%20or%20about%20%241%2C730.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%20airport%20in%20Muscat%2C%20my%20agent%20found%20me%20a%20really%20kind%20driver%20who%20took%20me%20to%20the%20border%20for%20about%20%24430%20in%20under%20four%20hours.%20It%20was%20smooth%2C%20there%20was%20no%20traffic%2C%20and%20the%20views%20of%20the%20mountains%20on%20the%20way%20to%20the%20border%20from%20the%20airport%20were%20so%20beautiful%20and%20peaceful.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20from%20the%20UAE%20border%20to%20my%20home%2C%20I%20had%20a%20taxi%20driver%20I've%20worked%20with%20before%20pick%20me%20up.%20The%20two-hour-long%20journey%20cost%20me%20about%20%24250.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReturning%20to%20family%20was%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffamily-living-abroad-abu-dhabi-united-arab-emirates-kids-war-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehuge%20relief%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Apart%20from%20my%20son%2C%20I%20have%20a%20nine-year-old%20Pomeranian%20at%20home%2C%20and%20he's%20been%20in%20my%20life%20for%20a%20long%20time.%20I%20also%20care%20deeply%20for%20my%20nanny%3B%20I%20would%20not%20just%20leave%20her%20behind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fembed.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDVYETCygOoL%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDVYETCygOoL%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDVYETCygOoL%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Nicky%20Lazou%20(%40nickylazou)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EI%20feel%20shocked%20because%20I%20never%20thought%20I%20would%20experience%20this%20in%