Brooklyn.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699e88fee8408f667180362b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222549%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Fort%20Greene%20Family%20Center%2C%20a%20Brooklyn%20homeless%20shelter%2C%20has%20105%20units%20for%20families%20with%20kids.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Westhab%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20new%20Brooklyn%20shelter%20offers%20apartment-style%20transitional%20housing%20for%20formerly%20homeless%20families.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20building%20could%20be%20turned%20into%20permanent%20housing%20if%20shelter%20demand%20falls.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENotably%2C%20the%20shelter%20faced%20little%20opposition%20from%20the%20community%2C%20its%20owner%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAcross%20the%20street%20from%20Brooklyn's%20leafy%20Fort%20Greene%20Park%2C%20dozens%20of%20formerly%20homeless%20families%20with%20children%20have%20found%20new%20temporary%20homes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20October%2C%20Marvina%20Brinkman%2C%2035%2C%20and%20her%20four%20children%20have%20stayed%20in%20a%20one-bedroom%20unit%20at%20the%20Fort%20Greene%20Family%20Center%20as%20Brinkman%20got%20on%20her%20feet%20and%20looked%20for%20permanent%20housing.%20She%20said%20the%20Center%20has%20helped%20her%20kids%20get%20into%20new%20schools%2C%20arranged%20transportation%2C%20and%20helped%20her%20look%20for%20permanent%20housing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20first%20shelter%20I've%20been%20in%20that%20I've%20actually%20gotten%20real%20help%20for%20me%20and%20my%20children%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20week%2C%20Brinkman%20and%20her%20children%20are%20moving%20into%20a%20permanent%20home%20a%20few%20miles%20away%20in%20Brownsville%2C%20Brooklyn.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%2473%20million%20facility%2C%20which%20opened%20last%20September%2C%20looks%20like%20any%20other%20gray%20brick%20Brooklyn%20apartment%20tower.%20That's%20until%20you%20glimpse%20the%2011-story%20mural%20of%20a%20little%20girl%20balancing%20books%2C%20a%20globe%2C%20and%20a%20teddy%20bear%20on%20a%20box%20of%20school%20supplies.%20The%20image%2C%20painted%20by%20the%20muralist%20and%20painter%20DaFlemingo%2C%20sets%20the%20building%20apart%20from%20most%20other%20homeless%20shelters%2C%20which%20often%20attempt%20to%20blend%20into%20neighborhoods%20that%20don't%20always%20want%20them%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Center%20also%20departs%20from%20traditional%20shelters%20in%20its%20interior%20design.%20All%20of%20the%20building's%20studios%20and%20one-%20and%20two-bedroom%20units%20function%20as%20private%20living%20spaces%2C%20each%20with%20its%20own%20bathroom%20and%20kitchen.%20They%20look%20like%20standard%2C%20albeit%20small%2C%20New%20York%20City%20apartments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you're%20on%20the%20inside%2C%20it%20looks%20like%20a%20normal%20apartment%20building%2C%26quot%3B%20Brinkman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22931%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20facade%20of%20the%20Westhab%20Family%20Center%20in%20Fort%20Greene%2C%20Brooklyn.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699e887f50f42603b0f8da89%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Westhab%20Family%20Center%20in%20Fort%20Greene%2C%20Brooklyn%2C%20has%20105%20units%20for%20families.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Westhab%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20most%20homeless%20shelters%20in%20the%20city%2C%20many%20of%20which%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwagner.nyu.edu%2Ffiles%2Fnyc2025%2FRosenbaum_Housing%2520and%2520Safe%2520Shelters_NYC%25202025_112921.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erepurposed%20commercial%20buildings%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20hotels%2C%20the%20building%20was%20designed%20to%20create%20transitional%20housing%20that%20could%20easily%20be%20transformed%20into%20permanent%20affordable%20housing%2C%20according%20to%20Westhab%2C%20the%20nonprofit%20that%20owns%20and%20operates%20the%20Fort%20Greene%20shelter%20%E2%80%94%20along%20with%20many%20others%20in%20the%20city%20and%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20city's%20Department%20of%20Social%20Services%20said%20the%20building%20%26quot%3Bexemplifies%20the%20city's%20ongoing%20commitment%20to%20transforming%20the%20shelter%20system%2C%26quot%3B%20by%20allowing%20the%20nonprofit%20provider%20to%20both%20own%20and%20operate%20a%20purpose-built%20building.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECritics%20of%20New%20York%20City's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2026%2F02%2F27%2Fopinion%2Fnew-york-homelessness-mamdani.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehomeless%20shelter%20system%3C%2Fa%3E%20say%20that%20without%20more%20supportive%20permanent%20housing%20for%20people%20experiencing%20homelessness%20or%20living%20on%20the%20brink%20of%20it%2C%20the%20city's%20unhoused%20population%20will%20only%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fgothamist.com%2Fnews%2Fnumber-of-street-homeless-new-yorkers-rises-as-city-braces-for-federal-funding-cuts%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econtinue%20to%20balloon%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20feeding%20a%20bloated%20system%20that%20too%20often%20prioritizes%20temporary%20support%20over%20long-term%20solutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20demand%20for%20shelters%20diminishes%2C%20the%20Center's%20units%20could%20be%20turned%20into%20permanent%2C%20affordable%20housing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20families%20who%20live%20here%20now%20%E2%80%94%20we%20could%20give%20them%20leases%2C%26quot%3B%20Richard%20Nightingale%2C%20CEO%20of%20Westhab%2C%20said%20during%20a%20recent%20tour%20of%20the%20building.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2290eabcd4-9211-49aa-9fb8-49219334dd78%5C%22%3EAnti-shelter%20NIMBYism%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAnti-development%20sentiment%20%E2%80%94%20also%20known%20as%20%26quot%3BNot%20in%20my%20backyard%26quot%3B%20or%20NIMBYism%20%E2%80%94%20can%20be%20tricky%20for%20housing%20advocates%20and%20developers%20to%20navigate.%20Homeless%20shelters%20tend%20to%20provoke%20the%20fiercest%20NIMBY%20backlash%20of%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWesthab%20has%20been%20caught%20in%20a%20series%20of%20high-pitched%20battles%20over%20its%20shelters%20across%20the%20city.%20It%20took%20four%20years%20and%20a%20protracted%20legal%20fight%20to%20open%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thecity.nyc%2F2021%2F11%2F10%2Fmanhattan-billionaires-row-homeless-shelter-opens-after-legal-battle%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshelter%20for%2080%20unhoused%20men%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20West%2058th%20Street%20%E2%80%94%20also%20known%20as%20Billionaires'%20Row%20%E2%80%94%20in%20Manhattan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225461%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20inside%20of%20a%20unit%20in%20the%20Fort%20Greene%20Family%20Center%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a1e7a3d3e2f1aef369b144%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223643%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20inside%20of%20a%20unit%20in%20the%20Fort%20Greene%20Family%20Center.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Westhab%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Sheepshead%20Bay%2C%20Brooklyn%2C%20local%20homeowners%20and%20residents%20organized%20months%20of%20demonstrations%20against%20a%20169-unit%20shelter%20for%20families%20with%20children.%20Residents%20erected%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbrooklyn.news12.com%2Fi-want-it-to-go-away-encampments-to-protest-planned-shelter-in-sheepshead-bay-enter-2nd-month%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ean%20encampment%3C%2Fa%3E%20next%20to%20the%20project%20site%2C%20and%20Westhab%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbsnews.com%2Fnewyork%2Fnews%2Fsheepshead-bay-brooklyn-proposed-homeless-shelter-westhab%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DWesthab%2520and%2520NYC%2520respond%2Chousing%2520plan%2520they%2520were%2520promised.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esued%20protesters%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20stop%20them%20from%20blocking%20access%20to%20the%20construction%20site.%20While%20the%20shelter%2C%20which%20is%20moving%20forward%2C%20is%20designed%20to%20house%20families%2C%20critics%20say%20the%20building%20shouldn't%20be%20located%20near%20schools%20or%20even%20in%20a%20residential%20neighborhood.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHomeless%20shelters%20don't%20belong%20in%20our%20residential%20neighborhoods%2C%20period%2C%26quot%3B%20State%20Sen.%20Stephen%20Chan%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nysenate.gov%2Fnewsroom%2Fpress-releases%2F2025%2Fstephen-t-chan%2Fsenator-chan-vehemently-opposes-homeless-shelter%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%20last%20year%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BSheepshead%20Bay%20is%20not%20a%20dumping%20ground.%20It%20is%20a%20neighborhood.%20It%20is%20our%20home%20to%20elderly%2C%20to%20children%20and%20families.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENightingale's%20response%3A%20%26quot%3BWhy%20would%20it%20be%20inappropriate%20to%20put%20a%20family%20building%20next%20to%20a%20school%3F%20It'd%20be%20incredibly%20appropriate.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20Sheepshead%20Bay%20shelter%20is%20finished%2C%20it%20will%20be%20the%20first%20in%20the%20area%20%E2%80%94%20part%20of%20a%20long-term%20effort%20by%20the%20City%20government%20to%20more%20equally%20distribute%20homeless%20shelters%20across%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Fort%20Greene%20shelter%20sits%20across%20the%20street%20from%20a%20public%20school%20and%20a%20library.%20It's%20minutes%20from%20multiple%20subway%20and%20bus%20lines%2C%20and%20has%20great%20access%20to%20jobs%20in%20Brooklyn%20and%20Manhattan.%20Notably%2C%20the%20shelter%20faced%20virtually%20no%20local%20opposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20no%20reason%20why%20affluent%20neighborhoods%20should%20be%20able%20to%20restrict%20these%20things%20because%20they%20lawyer%20up%20and%20a%20lower-income%20Black%20and%20Brown%20neighborhood%20gets%20its%2019th%20shelter%2C%26quot%3B%20Nightingale%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2F